# Portfolio Design System - Brutalist Aesthetic

## Core Design Principles

### Colors

- Background: `bg-white`
- Text: `text-black`
- Accent: `bg-yellow-400` (hover states, badges)
- Secondary text: `text-black/70`
- Borders: `border-black`

### Typography

- Headings: `font-bold uppercase` with sizes `text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl`
- Labels: `text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide`
- Body: `text-lg sm:text-xl text-black/70`
- Line height: `leading-tight` (headings), `leading-relaxed` (body)

### Spacing

- Sections: `py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24`
- Container: `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Elements: `space-y-8 lg:space-y-12` or `gap-4`

### Borders (Brutalist)

- Primary: `brutalist-border` (4px solid)
- Thin: `brutalist-border-thin` (2px solid)
- Section dividers: `border-b-4 border-black`

## Component Patterns

### Section Header

```tsx
<div className="mb-12 lg:mb-16">
  <div className="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-yellow-400 brutalist-border mb-4">
    <span className="font-bold text-black uppercase text-sm tracking-wide">
      Badge Text
    </span>
  </div>
  <h2 className="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-black mb-4">
    SECTION TITLE
  </h2>
  <p className="text-lg sm:text-xl text-black/70 max-w-3xl">
    Description
  </p>
</div>
```

### Interactive Card

```tsx
<div className="group brutalist-border bg-white p-6 hover:bg-black transition-all duration-300">
  <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-black group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
    Title
  </h3>
  <p className="text-sm text-black/70 group-hover:text-white/70 transition-colors">
    Content
  </p>
</div>
```

### Primary Button

```tsx
<button className="px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase text-sm bg-black text-white brutalist-border hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-black transition-all duration-300">
  BUTTON TEXT →
</button>
```

### Secondary Button

```tsx
<button className="px-8 py-4 font-bold uppercase text-sm bg-white text-black brutalist-border hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
  BUTTON TEXT
</button>
```

### Icon Button

```tsx
<button className="p-3 brutalist-border bg-white hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-all duration-300">
  <Icon className="w-5 h-5" />
</button>
```

### Form Input

```tsx
<label className="block text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">
  Label
</label>
<input className="block w-full px-4 py-4 text-black bg-white brutalist-border focus:bg-yellow-400/20 focus:outline-none transition-colors" />
```

## Key Rules

### ✅ Do's

- Use uppercase for headings, buttons, labels
- Apply tracking-wide to uppercase text
- Use yellow (#FACC15) for accents
- Keep borders thick (2px/4px)
- Use duration-300 for transitions
- Maintain consistent spacing
- Use group hover patterns

### ❌ Don'ts

- No rounded corners
- No soft shadows (use hard offsets)
- No gradients
- No thin borders (<2px)
- No mixed accent colors
- No lowercase for headings/buttons

## Hover Patterns

- Cards: `hover:bg-black` → text to white
- Buttons: `hover:bg-yellow-400`
- Icons: Add `group-hover:translate-x-2`
- Always use `transition-all duration-300`

## Responsive Pattern

```
text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl  // Headings
text-lg sm:text-xl                 // Body
py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24           // Sections
```

